sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application<br/>(in TEE)
    participant CDH as Confidential Data Hub<br/>(localhost:8006)
    participant AA as Attestation Agent<br/>(in TEE)
    participant KBS as Trustee KBS
    participant AS as Attestation Service
    participant Coll as Collateral Service<br/>(PCCS for TDX)
    participant GPU as GPU CC Manager<br/>(GPU only)
    participant Vault as HashiCorp Vault

    Note over App,CDH: Application requests secret
    App->>CDH: GET /cdh/resource/default/secret-name
    CDH->>AA: Request TEE evidence

    alt Intel TDX
        AA->>AA: Generate TDX quote
        AA->>Coll: Request attestation collateral
        Coll->>AA: Return PCK cert + TCB info
    else AMD SEV-SNP
        AA->>AA: Generate SEV-SNP report
        Note over AA: AMD uses cert chain (no PCCS)
    end

    opt NVIDIA GPU Present
        AA->>GPU: Request GPU attestation evidence
        GPU->>AA: Return GPU quote + CC mode status
    end

    AA->>CDH: Return combined evidence
    CDH->>KBS: Attest with evidence + request secret

    KBS->>AS: Verify attestation evidence
    AS->>AS: Validate TEE type<br/>(TDX / SEV-SNP / GPU)
    AS->>AS: Check PCR measurements<br/>against policy
    AS->>AS: Verify image signature<br/>(if signed policy enabled)
    AS->>KBS: Attestation result (pass/fail)

    alt Attestation Success
        KBS->>Vault: Fetch secret
        Vault->>KBS: Return secret
        KBS->>CDH: Encrypted secret
        CDH->>App: Secret (plaintext in TEE)
        Note over App: Application uses secret<br/>within protected memory
    else Attestation Failure
        KBS->>CDH: Error: Attestation failed
        CDH->>App: Error response
        Note over App: Secret not released
    end
